      "title": "The bardeen model as a nonlinear magnetic monopole",
      "abstract": "Abstract The Bardeen model — the first regular black hole model in General Relativity — is reinterpreted as the gravitational field of a nonlinear magnetic monopole, i.e., as a magnetic solution to Einstein equations coupled to a nonlinear electrodynamics."
